{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":2,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":1,"id":758,"created_at":"2015-10-18T18:33:50+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-18T18:33:50+0200","body":"<p>Les protections juridiques contre la diffusion publique d&#39;informations ne s&#39;appliquent pas aux informations d&#39;int&eacute;r&ecirc;t g&eacute;n&eacute;ral pour le public.<\/p>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":1,"author":{"username":"Bernard vAUQUELIN","displayName":"Bernard vAUQUELIN","uniqueId":"bernardvauquelin","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/bernardvauquelin","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":88,"title":"Section 3","subtitle":"Donn\u00e9es d\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eat g\u00e9n\u00e9ral","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[{"isContribuable":false,"id":5990,"body":"Comment et qui juge que ce sont des infos utiles. Autant d\u00e9noncer aux instances pr\u00e9vues pour cela.","created_at":"2015-10-18T18:49:22+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-18T18:49:22+0200","is_enabled":true,"votes_count":1,"type":0,"is_trashed":false,"author":{"username":"Jeanne Varasco","displayName":"Jeanne Varasco","uniqueId":"jeannevarasco","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/139_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/jeannevarasco","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"_links":{"show":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/consultations\/projet-de-loi-numerique\/consultation\/consultation\/opinions\/section-3-donnees-d-in